Description
PT Home Centre Indonesia is biggest and most complete furnishings retail company in Indonesia. We provide imported, high-quality furniture to fulfill high end customer's tastes. This year, we have growing to 44 stores with more than 6000 employees. For our aggressive expansion, we challenge professional people with Excellence, Leadership, Integrity, Team work, and Enthusiasm (ELITE)
Requirements
Diutamakan Pria, usia maksimal 30 tahun Pendidikan minimal SMU/SMK atau sederajat Pengalaman kerja di bidang yang sama minimal 1 tahun Berpengalaman melakukan pemasangan POP, media promosi dan layout display toko dan membuat laporan hasil pemasangan Bersedia bekerja shift time
All applications will be treated confidentially & only short listed candidates will be notified   Please click "Apply Now" button to apply
